        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 section1" style="opacity:0">
                <h2 style="color:#29AAE2">1 &gt; Zap</h2>  
                <p style="text-align:justify">
                    Simply enter your long URL in the box above and then click on the <em>Zap URL</em> button to convert it into a much shorter zap.in URL.
                    You may zap as many URLs as you like, each one will be tracked separately.<br />
                    We also have a simple but powerful <a href="apidocs">developer API</a> that you are free to use to zap your URLs.
                </p>              
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 section2" style="opacity:0">
                <h2 style="color:#29AAE2">2 &gt; Share</h2>                
                <p style="text-align:justify">
                    Share your zap.in URL wherever you like!<br /> 
                    For example you could post it on your favourite social network (Facebook, Twitter etc) or publish it on your own website or blog.
                    You could even advertise it on the <a href="https://mellowads.com" target="_blank">Mellow Ads</a> banner/pop-under advertising network (or your preferred ad network!)
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 section3" style="opacity:0">
                <h2 style="color:#29AAE2">3 &gt; Earn</h2>
                <p style="text-align:justify">
                    You can earn bitcoin for all unique, verified visitors to your zap.in URLs.
                    Earnings are paid daily and our aim is to pay out more than any other competitor services.<br />
                    NOTE: Zap.in is powered by <a href="https://mellowads.com" target="_blank">Mellow Ads</a> so you must register with a Mellow Ads account to earn from your zap.in URLs.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div> 
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12 section4" style="opacity:0">
                <h2 style="color:#29AAE2">What is zap.in?</h2>  
                <p style="text-align:justify">
                    Zap.in is a completely free link-shortening service which allows you to EARN BITCOIN from your links!
                    You can use our service just to zap your long URLs and convert them into much more convenient short URLs - and optionally you can earn revenue from each person that visits your zap.in URL.<br />
                    Zap.in is powered by <a href="https://mellowads.com" target="_blank">Mellow Ads</a> - the number 1 bitcoin banner and pop-under advertising network. 
                    This means that you can take advantage of Mellow Ads powerful statistics and performance analytics for your links and manage/withdraw your daily earnings whenever you like - direct to your bitcoin wallet!
                </p>
                <hr />
                <p style="text-align:center">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>&nbsp;Learn more about zap.in on our <a href="faq">FAQ</a> page
